The paper discusses the design and implementation of a distributed database, which falls under the categories of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), and Operating Systems (cs.OS). The paper also discusses the use of the Paxos algorithm, which falls under the category of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and System and Control Theory (cs.SY).
